Privacy Policy
Effective Date: February 21, 2017
This Privacy Policy demonstrates Kite Games Studio Ltd.'s commitment to protecting your privacy and addressing privacy-related concerns. Please review this policy regularly, as it may be updated from time to time. Updates will apply to information collected while the policy was in effect. If you have questions or comments regarding this Privacy Policy, contact us at
support@kitegamesstudio.com
.
Information Collection and Use
Kite Games Studio Ltd. does not collect personal information, such as names, addresses, phone numbers, email addresses, or specific locations, unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., during website registration).
We use analytics tools, such as the Facebook SDK, to gather data about app usage. This helps us understand feature usage and improve the app based on your experience. We do not collect personally identifiable information through these tools.
Children's Privacy
Children under 13 are not eligible to use our services, and we request that minors do not submit personal information. Minors may use the service only with the consent and supervision of a parent or guardian. If we discover that a child under 13 has provided personally identifiable information, we will delete it immediately.
Cookies
We use "cookie" technology to collect non-personal website usage data, enhance site functionality, and improve our services.
Session Cookies
: Enable features during a single visit and are deleted when you leave the website.
Persistent Cookies
: Remain on your computer after the browser is closed and are used on future visits. These can be managed or removed through your browser settings.
Cookies do not harm your computer and help us understand user interaction with our website. You can disable cookies through your browser settings; however, some site features may not function properly.
Information Sharing and Disclosure
Kite Games Studio Ltd. does not sell or rent personal information to third parties. If this policy changes in the future, you will have the option to opt out by contacting
support@kitegamesstudio.com
.
We may share non-personally identifiable information with third-party advertising companies to serve relevant ads. These third parties may use information about your visits to our site to provide targeted advertisements.
Third-Party Service Providers
We use the following third-party services within our apps:
AdMob
Google Analytics for Firebase
Firebase
For details about their privacy practices, refer to their respective privacy policies.
Compliance with Laws and Law Enforcement
Kite Games Studio Ltd. cooperates with law enforcement and third parties to enforce intellectual property rights and comply with legal obligations. We may disclose your information if necessary to:
Respond to legal claims or processes (e.g., subpoenas).
Protect the property, rights, or safety of Kite Games Studio Ltd., third parties, or the public.
Address illegal, unethical, or legally actionable activities.
Facial Data Usage
Certain apps by Kite Games Studio Ltd. use face data to detect facial landmarks for enhanced editing and user experience.
Data Storage
: We do not store facial data.
Data Sharing
: We do not share facial data with any third parties.
This data is processed solely on your device to ensure privacy.
Changes to the Privacy Policy
Kite Games Studio Ltd. reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. Changes will take effect immediately upon posting on our website. Regularly review this policy to stay informed about updates.
This Privacy Policy does not create any contractual or legal rights on behalf of any party. For concerns about privacy issues, contact us at
support@kitegamesstudio.com
.
Thank you for trusting Kite Games Studio Ltd. with your privacy. Your concerns are important to us.
